Martin:

Regarding your test for multivariate polynomial
multiplication:

On my machine (Windows), I got:
   [[10,1], [10,0], [10,1], [10,0], [10,1],
    [20,2], [20,2], [20,1], [20,1],[20,2],
    [30,4], [30,4], [30,3], [30,4], [30,4],
