which is painfully slow. Using DMP instead of POLY INT is
slightly faster:
 [[10,1], [10,0], [10,0], [10,0], [10,0],
[20,1], [20,1], [20,1], [20,1],[20,1],
[30,2], [30,3], [30,2], [30,3], [30,3],
